casebody.data:
First Department,

June, 1992

(June 1, 1992) In the Matter of J. Nicholas Tlaga, an Attorney.

Motion to reopen proceeding for further consideration, and for other relief, denied with leave to renew upon a showing of cooperation with the Departmental Disciplinary Committee, before whom respondent is directed to appear within 30 days from the date of entry of this Court’s order, all as indicated. Concur—Murphy, P. J., Milonas, Kupferman, Smith and Rubin, JJ.
